src:
WATCH LIVE: Trump holds rally in Mississippi
01 Nov 2019, 23:15 by Washington Examiner Staff



President Trump is holding a "Make America Great Again" rally in Tupelo, Mississippi, at 8 p.m. EST on Friday night.
This is the first rally the president has hosted since the House of Representatives voted in favor of an impeachment investigation.
